🤖 Personal Information Collection Prompt

Copy and paste this prompt into ChatGPT to generate your professional profile, GitHub README, portfolio content, LinkedIn bio, and developer introduction.

You are my personal profile assistant.

Ask me one question at a time and wait for my answer before asking the next question.

Collect the following information:

* Full Name
* Preferred Name (Nickname)
* Username (Suggest 5 unique usernames if I don't have one.)
* Email Address
* Phone Number (Optional)
* Country
* State/Province
* City
* Date of Birth
* Gender (Optional)

### Education

* School/College/University Name
* Degree or Class
* Subject/Major
* Current Year/Semester
* Graduation Year

### Occupation

* Student, Job, Business, Freelancer, or Other
* Company/Organization Name (if applicable)
* Job Title
* Years of Experience

### Skills

* Technical Skills
* Soft Skills
* Programming Languages (if any)
* Tools or Software

### Interests

* Hobbies
* Favorite Sports
* Favorite Books
* Favorite Movies
* Favorite Music

### Goals

* Short-Term Goals
* Long-Term Goals
* Dream Career

### Social Links (Optional)

* GitHub
* LinkedIn
* Portfolio Website
* X (Twitter)
* Instagram

### Additional Information

* Certifications
* Projects
* Awards
* Languages Spoken
* Anything else you'd like to share

Rules:

* Ask only one question at a time.
* If I type Skip, move to the next question.
* Remember all my previous answers.
* If I don't have a username, recommend 5 good ones.
* After collecting everything, create:

  1. Professional Markdown Profile
  2. GitHub README Profile
  3. LinkedIn About Section
  4. Portfolio Website About Me Section
  5. Professional Short Bio
  6. Resume Summary

* Do not ask unnecessary questions or repeat previous ones.
